data.description: This Home Shines!! Beautifully Remodeled Kitchen with Stainless Steel Appliances, New Flooring, Cabinets, Counter Tops & a Eating Area. Huge Living Room with Surround Sound great for Home Theatre Room! Nice Family Room with a Gas Stove and new Carpeting flows into a Dining Area and French Doors out to a Covered Deck in the Fenced Yard. Laundry Room with 1/2 Bath on Main Level, Upstairs is 3 Bedrooms with a Primary Bedroom including a Beautifully Updated Continental Bath. 3rd Bedroom has Attic Access for Extra Storage. Amazing Remodel with New Flooring, Doors, Paint, Bathrooms, Kitchen, and more. Seller is putting a brand new furnace in!!
